{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01WpkPdw42vdvUijd9Gbpak8","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Hvr8PWM13PrEV1c285RebZ","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-27\n\n### Session 29","new_string":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-27\n\n### Session 30 — state corruption fix #14, no-op (2026-03-27T19:27Z)\n\n- **State corruption fix #14**: Same pattern — 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 at `review`, phantom `1-1-foo` present, counts 75/70.\n- Root cause fix IS in dist/index.js:2313 (`clean.startsWith(\"{\")` guard). The fix was built in session 29's commit.\n- **Why corruption persists**: Ralph likely ran between session 29's commit and this session, using the OLD dist/ before session 29 rebuilt. The corruption is from a previous ralph iteration that ran before the fix was deployed.\n- Fixed: restored all 4 stories to `done`, removed phantom, counts to 74/74.\n- **This should be the LAST occurrence** — the fix is now in dist/ and committed.\n- All 74 stories done. No actionable work. Sprint complete.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: ~15\n- By tool: Read: 5, Edit: 6, Grep: 3, Glob: 2, Agent: 1, Bash: 1\n- Files read: 4 unique, 6 total reads\n- Redundant operations: Re-read of sprint-status.yaml due to concurrent modification\n\n### Session 29"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3622,"cache_read_input_tokens":56867,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3622},"output_tokens":73,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e4bb6cc1-84a5-45a0-af27-144a47ebc903","uuid":"13a62b9e-080d-48e8-b8cd-c3d5e3d10167"}
